name: Santa's Large Combo (SL Combo)
description: The first Combo in our menu is the order from Santa Claus himself (@PixelSantas) that asked for two doubles large, fries, cookies and a cup of milk for dessert. We added a large coke because everything got better with coke. But to have it, you need to be a nice kid. Note: HLE= "Happiness level after eat it"
